<b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=157822>Caave Monster's Profile</a></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/uasunnyday.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Asun Nyday</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beast Prince</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#871F78>(6/17/02 12:51:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=569.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Beastlord Only Equiptment</span><hr size=1> Well, there's four sets of velious, a set of kunark and a set of luclin armor that jump to mind immediately. Also the multiple weapons and cloaks from the shar vahl beastmaster class quests. The Epic weapons, pre-epic weapons, etc. Most if not all weapons with Eitchatka or Pitchatka in the name. Some of the Claw weapons.<br>
<br>
