<br>
If its just for curiosity's sake then .. yah, you got Thurg, Skyshrine, Kael, Plane of Growth, Fear, Kunark, Twilight Sea, and SharVal class quests to get you all the main BST only gear.  The h2h have 8 billion screaming monks keeping us from getting much in the class specific line.<br>
