<br>
But more to the point..we should make a list of items that should have BST on them but do not. The list would be long.  There are 1HB weapons all over that are melee/hybrid usable but not BST.  Armor is another thing.  Like why can't a BST wear Silver Chitin Wristguards?  We can wear the gloves just fine.  But not the bracer with its 15 AC +7 str/dex and 40 hp.  That just makes no sense to me at all.   And do not even get me started on the fungi tunic thing.<br>
<br>
If verant wants to treat us like a mutt class then they need to allow us to wear the mutt armor just like the rest of the hybrid community. <p>Vecsus Strangiato <br>
