Tarew Marr <br>
http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212314 </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/udando.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dando</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beast Regent</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#871F78>(6/17/02 8:51:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=569.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Beastlord Only Equiptment</span><hr size=1> Yes, the Savage Lord's Pitchatka is still Beast only.  I should have been clearer actually.  My point here is to find out what high end gear; such as drops from God level mobs in Luclin, that are Beast only useable.  Why?  Because then there are less people interested in that particuaral item(s).<br>
